# Custom profile - your own starting point.
#
# Copy any `brew "..."`, `cask "..."`, `vscode "..."`, or `npm "..."` line
# from the root Brewfile (or add new ones) and this profile will install
# exactly that set via:
#
#   ./bootstrap.sh --profile custom
#   # or
#   ./dev install --profile custom
#
# Empty by default - `brew bundle` against an empty Brewfile is a safe
# no-op, it just installs nothing.
